OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fthrough the evening with clear spells
OL,7,Fin the west but low cloud and mist
OL,8,Freturning to eastern coasts. Cloud and
OL,9,Fthe odd light shower into the north
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FStaying dry and warm in the
OL,13,Fwest with prolonged sunny spells.
OL,14,FCooler and cloudier in the northeast
OL,15,Fwith perhaps the odd spot of rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
