OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudier
OL,6,Fon Sunday with some showery outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain. Dry spells and chance of
OL,8,Fscattered showers developing on
OL,9,FMonday. Dry again Tuesday, warmer in
OL,10,Fwest, cooler in east.
